{"tid":1630520,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"人體生理學入門","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:46:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T13:23:26.000Z","uid":19984,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d69d37d895513add36d8b99c8bcddd3dfdf7dd15","tid":1630520,"uid":19984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:46:50.000Z","msg":"啱先見到旺角踢波，有個廢老自己跣低冚親個後腦！雖然條友仲清醒，但係流咗好多血。<br />\n<br />\n其實整親後腦係可大可小嘅，我諗大家都唔係想有人死，所以我喺度想呼籲大家睇睇以下嘅人體生理學入門。<br />\n<br />\n人嘅膝頭哥其實好脆弱，四條韌帶ACL，PCL，MCL，LCL其實都好易斷。踢波唔使好大力撞一撞或者被人一腳踢埋去就會斷㗎啦喇。<br />\n<br />\n以外面條韌帶 LCL 做例子(睇圖，幅圖係右腳膝頭哥)，喺側邊輕輕一踢其實就會斷。一斷就要搞返三四個月都唔知好唔好得返。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家做運動踢波打波嘅時候要小心啲，唔好撞親人地！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VzENvv3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVzENvv3.jpg&h=558ec746&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d240a566ba756d7426618a9585623abee8094ed1","tid":1630520,"uid":130079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:52:23.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"dc4a3c141aadf9e17d045837a3fc8b457dc18cc9","tid":1630520,"uid":19984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:03:05.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"0cd9db70b57b746e5c6f6299f56de264c788cda6","tid":1630520,"uid":19984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:12:05.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"e268655de9f7386b807afbec4d8e35c6d3e4068a","tid":1630520,"uid":19984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:12:15.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"25e1fd23c6e61c2be3257cc5d96821ebdc036112","tid":1630520,"uid":19984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:20:52.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"c9372c7026aa780aff4639287209cf3e0bb578b0","tid":1630520,"uid":19984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:21:09.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"565310b164e08fa36c5073a31584f626fee13e8d","tid":1630520,"uid":19984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:21:22.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"525d4fa45c7c06e05fc38580cd676ac4f65885f5","tid":1630520,"uid":19984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:22:11.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"7a3e36b4ba46d10cb95a8a1e3139b28dbe6189ba","tid":1630520,"uid":19984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:22:24.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"848beea9620940b4b00d2fa7f733c24ed8368027","tid":1630520,"uid":19984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:22:50.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"459ed2919e3217c6ca309530c74a0e08e3c1104d","tid":1630520,"uid":19984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:23:26.000Z","msg":"10/10"}]}